<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <p>Hello {{ name }},</p>

    <p>
        The build job for <b>{{ service_name }}</b> has completed with status:
        <b style="color: {% if status == 'SUCCESS' %}green{% else %}red{% endif %};">
            {{ status }}
        </b>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Build Details:</strong></p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Build Number:</strong> {{ build_number }}</li>
        <li><strong>Build Time:</strong> {{ build_time }}</li>
        <li><strong>Services/Libraries:</strong> {{ service_name }}</li>
        <li><strong>Environment:</strong> {{ environment }}</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        For deployment approval, click below:
    </p>

    <p>
        <a href="{{ url }}" style="background-color:#007bff;color:white;padding:10px 15px;text-decoration:none;">
            Open Pipeline
        </a>
    </p>

    <br>

    <p>Thanks & Regards,<br>DevOps Team</p>

</body>
</html>
